Description:
   Psishield is the Egomancer's signature remort shield. It surrounds the
   caster in a pulsing psionic field that assaults the minds of attackers.
   Similar in structure to fireshield, it deals reactive mental-element
   damage while absorbing a portion of incoming damage.

   Shield properties:
     - Type: PSI_SHIELD (cannot stack with other non-coexisting shields)
     - Reactive Damage: 30% of incoming damage dealt back as mental damage
     - Absorption: 10% + (pseudo_level / 10)% of incoming damage absorbed
     - Hit Points: 5,000 + (pseudo_level * 10) -- shield breaks when depleted
     - Duration: pseudo_level / 10 rounds (halved on login)

   The reactive mental damage bypasses cloak reflection and absorption
   effects. Creatures without minds are immune to the reactive component.
